              MajorMUD Plus - Entertainment Edition
              -------------------------------------

MajorMUD Plus is an add-on package for the MajorMUD role-playing game.

It provides the following additional functionality for MajorMUD:

* User-definable character descriptions (with optional charge)
* Registries for MajorMUD characters
* Ability to purchase lives (optionally for credits, copper, or days)
* Offline action editor
* Global MajorMUD registry lookup (/mudreg)
